headline: 3 Reasons WFC is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Wells Fargo trades at $84 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, gaining 7.8% over the last six months. At the same time, the S&P 500 has returned 5.8%.
